00:04:26,265 --> 00:04:27,623
And did he give you a name?
他告诉你名字了吗

39
00:04:27,624 --> 00:04:29,463
No, just the code name.
没有 只告诉了我代号

40
00:04:29,464 --> 00:04:31,783
Keats. The Romantic poet.
济慈 就是那个浪漫主义诗人

41
00:04:31,784 --> 00:04:35,223
-I know who Keats was!  -There were five of them
-我知道济慈是谁  -他们总共五个人

42
00:04:35,224 --> 00:04:39,224
in the '80s who policed the trade unions and the like.
在80年代被部署在工会之类的地方

43
00:04:40,184 --> 00:04:43,143
He sent a text before he shot himself to the other four.
