我们认为他带上了Andy Fisher一起

82
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:22,220
Yes, it's DCS Ian St Clair here. Um...
喂 我是Ian St Clair总警司

83
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:25,897
I have a person of interest whose records are restricted,
我这里有一名嫌疑人的档案我无权查看

84
00:07:25,898 --> 00:07:27,858
