我需要解锁这份档案

85
00:07:29,018 --> 00:07:30,698
Yeah, the name I have is...
嗯 那个人的名字是

86
00:07:31,658 --> 00:07:33,298
..Helen St Clair.
Helen St Clair

87
00:07:39,778 --> 00:07:43,057
You have been recruited for this covert operation
你们被征召参与此次秘密行动

88
00:07:43,058 --> 00:07:45,976
