105
00:09:26,334 --> 00:09:27,533
Take 'em down!
把它们扯下来

106
00:09:27,534 --> 00:09:29,294
Solidarity, mate! That's what I'm...
团结 兄弟 我是想

107
00:09:41,653 --> 00:09:43,853
Gary? Can you get us a...?
Gary 能不能帮我们拿个

108
00:10:00,853 --> 00:10:03,293
-All right?  -Nice to see you, love.
-你还好吗  -很高兴见到你 亲爱的

109
00:10:12,132 --> 00:10:14,292
They lost the bloody game, Gary!
他们输掉了那场该死的比赛 Gary

110
00:10:15,572 --> 00:10:17,931
You two ganging up on me, as per usual.
你俩又联合起来反对我 跟往常一样

111
00:10:17,932 --> 00:10:19,131
I have work in the morning,
我明天还得上早班

112
00:10:19,132 --> 00:10:19,990
so this is my last drink, right?
所以我只能喝这最后一杯了 好吗

113
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:21,720
I'm going to get the violins out, Cathy.
你有什么好抱怨的 Cathy

114
