Here we go.
走起

117
00:10:29,972 --> 00:10:31,371
What have you crossed there for?
你干嘛猜那儿

118
00:10:31,372 --> 00:10:33,731
The players aren't even looking in that direction.
球员甚至都没往那个方向看

119
00:10:33,732 --> 00:10:35,450
Why not? That's where I want to put it,
这儿怎么了 我就想猜这儿

120
00:10:35,451 --> 00:10:38,211
