Clipstone 那儿不全是工贼吗

131
00:11:11,970 --> 00:11:13,769
No, not my old man.
我爸可不是

132
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:15,409
Bloody hell! He's like your Gary -
天哪 他跟你家Gary一样

133
00:11:15,410 --> 00:11:17,650
thinks a picket line is sacrosanct.
认为纠察线神圣不可侵犯

134
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:21,769
