不懂 太深奥了 我不理解

138
00:11:30,929 --> 00:11:32,088
It's "Sinclair",
发音是Sinclair

139
00:11:32,089 --> 00:11:33,768
not "Saint Clair".
不是圣Clair

140
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,180
Don't give 'em airs and graces they don't warrant
