151
00:12:10,688 --> 00:12:13,847
All right, treacle. Does it feel good, eh,
好吧 小可爱 感觉不错吧

152
00:12:13,848 --> 00:12:15,607
being a pawn in the tyrannical state?
做专制政府的马前卒

153
00:12:15,608 --> 00:12:17,607
Maggie's boot boys!
撒切尔的擦鞋童

154
00:12:24,288 --> 00:12:27,727
Scab! Scab! Scab! Scab! Scab!
工贼 工贼 工贼 工贼 工贼

155
00:12:46,967 --> 00:12:48,726
Piss off back to London!
滚回伦敦

156
00:13:23,925 --> 00:13:26,525
-Kevin?  -Yeah.
-Kevin  -嗯

157
00:13:28,925 --> 00:13:30,804
I, um...
我 呃

158
00:13:30,805 --> 00:13:33,685
..ordered you a beer. I wasn't sure.
给你点了杯啤酒 不知道你爱不爱喝

159
00:13:35,125 --> 00:13:36,485
Cheers.
谢谢

160
00:13:40,925 --> 00:13:42,964
Listen, um, I don't think I should be in the middle
