00:13:58,084 --> 00:13:59,203
Does Ian know?
Ian知道吗

166
00:13:59,204 --> 00:14:00,684
No-one knows.
没人知道

167
00:14:01,644 --> 00:14:02,964
Why?
为什么

168
00:14:04,004 --> 00:14:06,843
Because as soon as you tell just one other person,
因为一旦你告诉了任何一个人

169
00:14:06,844 --> 00:14:11,244
even the person you love most in the world, it starts to...
哪怕是这世上你最爱的人 你就会

170
00:14:12,484 --> 00:14:15,484
